    <h1 class="full-span not-bold">Having reviewed several existing carbon footprint calculators, we discovered that transportation was our largest source of carbon impact, and indeed is the largest source of carbon impact for most individuals in the UK.
    <br>
    <br>We decided to create a simple calculator based off the UK government <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/government-conversion-factors-for-company-reporting">carbon emissions conversion factors</a> where users can determine the carbon footprint of their travel based on an short questionaire.</h1>

