      <h2>UX Challenges</h2>
      <p>The biggest challenge of the project was creating an intuitive user experience for the complex branching structure of the form. We wanted it to be dynamically generated, so that the app could be updated with new transportation methods (such as space travel) over time.<br><br>
      This proved to be doubly challenging because the UK government resource for carbon emission factors of different transportation methods was an excell spreadsheet. To ensure our calculator worked seamlessly, we had to build our own API using MongoDB.</p>
